title: Journey Into Mystery, Vol. 4: The Manchester Gods
description: The MANCHESTER GODS dread URBAN PANTHESISM arises in the north of Otherworld, the British Subconscious! Don't look panicked. We just mean "Civil War." A Civil War that Asgardia refuses to interfere in. Publicly. Behind the scenes, Loki is a one-man intervention force. Also: Secret mission from Hela! COLLECTING: JOURNEY INTO MYSTERY 639-641, THE MIGHTY THOR ANNUAL 1
author: Kieron Gillen
